Lavish Spa vouchers offer a portfolio of spas and beauty salons, including many well-known locations such as PURE Spa, Malmaison, Luminis and launching in April Bannatyne Spa's. Lavish offers a gift of choice that lets you enjoy spending your voucher in exactly the way you please. Whether you are seeking a full day at a spa being pampered, a simple manicure or relaxing massage, a Lavish voucher has it covered.